## 7. Implementation Phases

### Phase 5A: Core Engine (Weeks 1-3)
**Goal:** Basic task chaining and state management

| Task | Owner | Deliverable |
|------|-------|-------------|
| State Store Implementation | Beta Manager | PostgreSQL schema + Redis caching |
| Workflow Engine Core | Beta Manager | DAG executor, step sequencer |
| Step-Router Integration | Gamma Manager | Target manager resolution |
| Basic API Endpoints | Delta Manager | CRUD for workflows/definitions |
| Serialization Spec | Gamma Manager | JSON schema validation |

**Milestone:** Single-manager sequential workflows working end-to-end.

### Phase 5B: Retry & Circuit Breaker (Weeks 4-5)
**Goal:** Resilient task execution

| Task | Owner | Deliverable |
|------|-------|-------------|
| Retry Manager | Beta Manager | Backoff algorithms, retry counters |
| Circuit Breaker | Beta Manager | Per-target CB state |
| Error Classification | Gamma Manager | Retryable vs non-retryable patterns |
| DLQ Foundation | Delta Manager | Storage + basic replay |
| Monitoring Hooks | Alpha Manager | Retry metrics, CB state changes |

**Milestone:** Failed tasks retry automatically; exhausted retries go to DLQ.

### Phase 5C: Priority & Escalation (Weeks 6-7)
**Goal:** Production-grade prioritization

| Task | Owner | Deliverable |
|------|-------|-------------|
| Priority Queue | Beta Manager | Multi-level queue structure |
| Aging Algorithm | Gamma Manager | Automatic escalation logic |
| Preemption Framework | Beta Manager | Graceful task interruption |
| SLA Enforcement | Gamma Manager | Deadline tracking, alerts |
| King AI Escalation | King AI | Escalation protocol |

**Milestone:** CRITICAL tasks preempt NORMAL tasks; deadlines trigger escalation.

### Phase 5D: Cross-Manager Chaining (Weeks 8-9)
**Goal:** End-to-end cross-functional workflows

| Task | Owner | Deliverable |
|------|-------|-------------|
| Cross-Manager Protocol | Gamma Manager | sessions_send integration |
| Manager Registration | King AI | Dynamic manager discovery |
| Capability Routing | Gamma Manager | Target by capability, not worker |
| Data Flow Pipeline | Beta Manager | Input/output mapping engine |
| Parallel Execution | Beta Manager | Fan-out/fan-in patterns |

**Milestone:** Research → Code → Test → Document workflow executes across all managers.

### Phase 5E: Production Hardening (Weeks 10-12)
**Goal:** Deployable system

| Task | Owner | Deliverable |
|------|-------|-------------|
| Observability Stack | Alpha Manager | Tracing, metrics, alerting |
| Security Review | King AI | Auth, audit logging |
| Load Testing | Delta Manager | Performance benchmarks |
| Documentation | Alpha Manager | Operator guides, troubleshooting |
| Migration Tool | Beta Manager | Phase 4 → Phase 5 conversion |

**Milestone:** System meets production readiness criteria (see Appendix B).

